{"type":"message","id":"4e4fe7ea","parentId":"9c72886d","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:28:10.688Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-03-28 22:28 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态，整理3-5条关键信息，保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md。文件应该包含：标题\"行业动态学习笔记\"、学习日期（2026年3月28日）、3-5条关键信息（每条包含标题、来源、摘要），以及学习心得。"}],"timestamp":1774708090685}}
{"type":"message","id":"599d5fac","parentId":"4e4fe7ea","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:28:18.238Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent task is to search for industry news related to 道简网络's business (企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务), compile 3-5 key pieces of information, and save them to a file.\n\nLet me search for relevant industry news using the web search skill.","thinkingSignature":"2c0e95dd3ebb78467d0d96698331de559da0db6f9ea7fc7328cca6562b451eb2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eljiajuivf75_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":104,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42098,"totalTokens":42319,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001248,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00505176,"total":0.00521166}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774708090687}}
{"type":"message","id":"9644c212","parentId":"599d5fac","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:28:18.244Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_eljiajuivf75_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774708098241}}
{"type":"message","id":"c6d08fc3","parentId":"9644c212","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:28:23.208Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll search for industry news related to 道简网络's business areas: 企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务.","thinkingSignature":"05904fee7640d45c58822e05cc8e05c7b2c73581e91f3b181d2c8dc93090dd23"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_stdetfw115ea_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新动态 政策\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_stdetfw115ea_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 弱电工程 2026行业动态\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_stdetfw115ea_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 网络系统集成 2026趋势\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":890,"output":188,"cacheRead":41944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43022,"cost":{"input":0.000267,"output":0.00022559999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0012583199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017509199999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774708098244}}
